spans.text: Her generous Breast scarce other Pleasure
Her generous Breast scarce other Pleasure
with strictest Prudence how to spend
frugal to herself , and noble to her Friend
Where wait the Poor , as their Distresses call : Nor call in vain ; but of Assistance sure ; If hungry , fed ; if sick , they find a Cure
wait the Poor , as their Distresses call : Nor call in vain ; but of Assistance sure ; If hungry , fed ; if sick , they find a Cure
Yet livelier Beauty in their native Soil
Part the Sun gilds , and Part the Shades imbrown
On Severn , proudly rolling back her Tides
On Severn , proudly rolling back her Tides
a dread Scene of War , and Blood , and Fire :
drenched the Meadows with a Crimson Tide
harmless on the level Green , The Noise of War is hushed
Nor Windsor Forest ever fair and gay , Immortalised by Pope's harmonious Lay
